my_library is a personal lending library app written with ruby on rails
models
-book
-person

controllers
-books_controller
-library_controller

how the app is structured
book attributes: title
		author
		upvotes/likes
		downvotes/dislikes
		summary
    association :person_id => belongs_to :person
person attributes: name
		   maximum books
	association :books => has_any :books

main methods in app
-add/remove_person
-add/remove_book
-checkuout_book
-checkin_book
-login/logout=> admin, user
-view_available_books


